Okay so I know Those Nights at Rachel's is not official FNAF canon; but I wanted to jump back into some FNAF themed jumpscares, and a lot of you have been suggesting this game. And even thought Scott himself did not make this game... it deserves some attention. The visuals are stunning and the added mechanics make the game that much more intense!
